uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model

Class CIdentity

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model.CIdentity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    DIdentity, OIdentity

    public class CIdentity
extends java.lang.Object
    Identifies a concept-level entity from the frames-based model via a unique identifier, and a label. The identifier must always be supplied, whereas the label is optional and will be assigned a default value if not supplied.
